Closest I have is [Social Gothic](http://web.archive.org/web/20150317063731/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/canadatype/social-gothic) mixing upper and lowercases. As Social Gothic is a revival of "Thomas Hollingworth’s Informal Gothic, one of the winners in VGC’s National Typeface Design competition in 1965." The time frame looks to match so could be Informal Gothic at its origin...

